      "name": "Primary stiffness QoI validation — non-cannulated construct",
      "description": "FEA-predicted construct stiffness was evaluated against the experimental ensemble mean from N=11 non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw specimens tested under ASTM F1717 static compression-bending. The normalized error metric E/uval was computed at 1.41, falling within the pre-established acceptance threshold of 1.96. The experimental dataset used for this comparison was collected under a displacement-controlled protocol at 5 mm/min crosshead speed, consistent with ASTM F1717 Section 8.4. Agreement is considered satisfactory and supports model credibility for the declared COU.",
      "quantityOfInterest": "Construct stiffness (N/mm)",
