      "rationale": "Validation specimens are the same non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw design as the COU device. ASTM F1717 test configuration is the regulatory standard for this device class. The validation activity is judged highly relevant to the COU. The single-condition limitation in Test Conditions is acknowledged but does not invalidate the overall validation relevance at this model risk level."
    }
